ZH: 我们能捐助一些钱给地震灾区吗？
EN: Can we donate some money to the earthquake-stricken areas?

ZH: 这个组织需要捐助物品和资金。
EN: The organization needs donations of goods and funds.

ZH: 我们应该积极捐助需要帮助的人。
EN: We should actively donate to those in need.

ZH: 他们在网上发起了一场捐助活动。
EN: They launched a donation campaign online.

ZH: 每一份捐助都会有所帮助。
EN: Every donation will make a difference.

ZH: 她总是很慷慨地捐助给慈善机构。
EN: She is always generous in donating to charity organizations.

ZH: 老师提议班级一起捐助给贫困学生。
EN: The teacher suggested the class donate to help poor students.

ZH: 他在生日时请求亲友们捐助给慈善机构。
EN: He requested friends and family to donate to charity on his birthday.

ZH: 他们筹备了一个慈善晚宴来募集捐助。
EN: They organized a charity banquet to raise donations.

ZH: 我们想要为救灾工作捐助一定的款项。
EN: We want to donate a certain amount of money for disaster relief work.

ZH: 昨天我捐助了一批孤儿院需要的物资。
EN: Yesterday I donated supplies needed by the orphanage.

ZH: 他家庭出现困难，我们应该伸出援手捐助一些金钱。
EN: His family is facing difficulties, we should lend a helping hand and donate some money.

ZH: 公司承诺每年捐助一定比例的利润给慈善事业。
EN: The company promised to donate a certain percentage of profits to charity every year.

ZH: 她从小就明白捐助和善心对他人的意义。
EN: She understood the meaning of donation and kindness to others from a young age.

ZH: 学校募集了一笔巨资，大家都积极捐助。
EN: The school raised a large sum of money, and everyone contributed actively.

ZH: 数十家公司的捐助使得这个活动得以顺利进行。
EN: Donations from dozens of companies made the event successful.

ZH: 我s想要参与这个项目，并捐助我的时间和精力。
EN: I want to get involved in this project and donate my time and energy.

ZH: 捐助是一种美德，可以帮助更多的人。
EN: Donation is a virtue that can help more people.

ZH: 孩子回收了废品然后出售来为救灾工作捐助。
EN: The child collected recyclables and sold them to donate to disaster relief work.

ZH: 我们应该常常思考如何可以多捐助一些帮助他人。
EN: We should often think about how we can donate more to help others.
